OL,3,CPensioner devastated after losing
OL,4,C#20,000 life savings in banking scam
OL,6,FAn Oxford pensioner who lost #20,000
OL,7,Fof his life savings to fraudsters says
OL,8,Fhe's "devastated" at falling for a con.
OL,10,FLeonard Adams from Cowley wants his
OL,11,Fmoney back after he was scammed into
OL,12,Ftransferring it out of his bank
OL,13,Faccount.
OL,15,FLloyd's Bank says it sympathises but
OL,16,Fis not returning the money, so he's
OL,17,Fnow reliant on his pension to make
OL,18,Fends meet.
