OL,6,FThe 71-year-old wants to raise
OL,7,Fawareness of how it can happen to
OL,8,Fanyone.
OL,10,FHe'd saved #25,000 for a lease
OL,11,Fextension on his flat, but a phone
OL,12,Fcall last August from a con artist
OL,13,Fclaiming to be Lloyds Bank pressured
OL,14,Fhim to transfer #20,000 of it to
OL,15,Fanother account.
OL,17,F"I never thought it would happen to me
OL,18,Fbecause I'm so careful.
