OL,6,FWhen he asked the bank to make the
OL,7,Ftransfer they asked him five questions
OL,8,Frelating to fraud.
OL,10,F"One of the questions was, did anybody
OL,11,Fask you to move your money, and I said
OL,12,Fno. So they've got me down as lying to
OL,13,Fthe bank."
