OL,6,F"So they reckon that is part of the
OL,7,Freason why they won't give me my money
OL,8,Fback, because I lied to the bank to
OL,9,Fstart with, and secondly because they
OL,10,Fthought I should have checked out the
OL,11,Fscammer a bit more."JThis type of
OL,12,Ffraud, where a scammer pretends to be
OL,13,Fyour bank, is called impersonation
OL,14,Ffraud.
