OL,6,FHe went back to the bank where staff
OL,7,Finformed him he'd been scammed.
OL,9,FThey attempted to stop the transfer
OL,10,Fbut only managed to save #500 of the
OL,11,F#20,000.
OL,13,FLloyds Bank is not returning the money.
OL,15,FLeonard says he's now struggling with
OL,16,Fhis health and is working with the
OL,17,Ffinancial ombudsman to see if there is
OL,18,Fmore he can do.
