OL,6,F"At the end of the day all I want is
OL,7,Fmy money back. If I could get my money
OL,8,Fback then nothing else matters."
OL,10,FLloyds bank says it sympathises with
OL,11,FLeonard and customers should always be
OL,12,Fwary of out the blue calls claiming to
OL,13,Fthe bank. They say your bank will
OL,14,Fnever ask you to move money to protect
